    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Buffett Rule Act of 2013 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow taxpayers to donate an amount (not less than $1), in addition to any tax owed, which shall be deposited in the general fund of the Treasury and transferred to an account used to reduce the public debt.&nbsp; Requires such donation to be designated on&nbsp;a taxpayer's income tax return at the time such return is filed.</p>]]></text>
